## üö® Red Flags - Stop Development

- **Keyboard inaccessible**: Any feature that can't be used keyboard-only
- **Screen reader failures**: Content not announced or confusing
- **Color-only information**: Critical info conveyed by color alone
- **Poor contrast**: Text that doesn't meet WCAG contrast requirements
- **Mobile unusable**: Features that don't work on mobile devices
- **Performance issues**: Slow loading or unresponsive interactions

